1
00:00:13,379 --> 00:00:15,020
In the days to come,

2
00:00:15,539 --> 00:00:18,099
I will love, cherish,

3
00:00:18,460 --> 00:00:20,899
and be faithful to him

4
00:00:21,020 --> 00:00:23,180
until death do us part.

5
00:00:23,180 --> 00:00:24,379
Do you take this man to be your lawful wedded husband?

6
00:00:30,620 --> 00:00:31,620
No.

7
00:00:35,419 --> 00:00:36,260
Don't worry.

8
00:00:36,859 --> 00:00:38,580
I don't want to marry him not because of Gu Chengjing,

9
00:00:39,220 --> 00:00:40,419
but because of

10
00:00:43,379 --> 00:00:44,260
Ji Xiaoxue.

11
00:01:17,219 --> 00:01:19,859
Gu Chengyan, you can abandon the woman you love the most

12
00:01:19,859 --> 00:01:21,939
for the position of chairman.

13
00:01:22,059 --> 00:01:23,460
How could I marry a man

14
00:01:23,460 --> 00:01:24,740
like you?

15
00:01:26,260 --> 00:01:27,299
Stop pretending.

16
00:01:27,779 --> 00:01:29,579
I told you long ago that

17
00:01:29,779 --> 00:01:32,380
Ji Xiaoxue is not your real sister.

18
00:01:37,219 --> 00:01:38,139
I never thought

19
00:01:38,820 --> 00:01:40,380
we'd come full circle

20
00:01:40,820 --> 00:01:42,100
and end up back where we started.

21
00:01:42,900 --> 00:01:43,859
If

22
00:01:44,820 --> 00:01:46,620
Ji Xiaoxue isn't your sister,

23
00:01:47,659 --> 00:01:49,299
would you still choose to marry me?

24
00:01:53,779 --> 00:01:54,579
What do you mean?

25
00:01:54,939 --> 00:01:56,219
I just want to say

26
00:01:57,340 --> 00:01:58,299
sometimes

27
00:01:58,859 --> 00:01:59,820
what you see

28
00:01:59,980 --> 00:02:00,779
and hear

29
00:02:01,740 --> 00:02:02,939
may not be true.

30
00:02:11,980 --> 00:02:12,500
Morning.

31
00:02:12,940 --> 00:02:13,579
Morning.

32
00:02:15,139 --> 00:02:16,459
Why don't you let the servants do it?

33
00:02:16,940 --> 00:02:18,179
I'm used to doing it myself.

34
00:02:19,459 --> 00:02:20,700
I can help you.

35
00:02:21,100 --> 00:02:23,299
You rich boys don't know how to do this.

36
00:02:24,339 --> 00:02:25,339
I do.

37
00:02:25,820 --> 00:02:26,700
Believe me.

38
00:02:26,859 --> 00:02:27,780
I'll show you.

39
00:02:27,780 --> 00:02:28,859
I'll do it myself.

40
00:02:28,859 --> 00:02:29,820
Let me try.

41
00:02:36,139 --> 00:02:37,419
Let me take you to bandage it.

42
00:02:38,500 --> 00:02:39,339
It's okay.

43
00:02:39,419 --> 00:02:41,060
It's common to get hurt when cooking.

44
00:02:42,899 --> 00:02:44,100
I should go.

45
00:02:44,299 --> 00:02:45,220
I don't want to bother you.

46
00:02:55,019 --> 00:02:55,899
Are you sure?

47
00:02:57,060 --> 00:02:58,940
She's not my biological daughter?

48
00:03:07,220 --> 00:03:08,019
Chengyan,

49
00:03:08,060 --> 00:03:09,339
don't listen to Wanqing.

50
00:03:09,739 --> 00:03:11,380
Xiaoxue is my biological daughter.

51
00:03:11,859 --> 00:03:12,660
Mr. Gu,

52
00:03:13,739 --> 00:03:15,619
I'm neither Ji Xiaoxue

53
00:03:16,060 --> 00:03:17,660
nor Liu Xiaoxue.

54
00:03:18,980 --> 00:03:22,019
I'm Su Wan, the daughter of Su Junmin,

55
00:03:24,540 --> 00:03:25,619
the owner of Su's Art Gallery.

56
00:03:32,019 --> 00:03:32,859
Xiaoxue,

57
00:03:33,500 --> 00:03:34,619
are you lying to me?

58
00:03:34,940 --> 00:03:36,500
Are you still mad at me?

59
00:03:37,780 --> 00:03:39,260
You don't deserve to be my father.

60
00:03:39,339 --> 00:03:41,060
My father is Su Junmin.

61
00:03:41,419 --> 00:03:43,419
When I knew something happened to my father,

62
00:03:43,540 --> 00:03:44,579
I was still abroad.

63
00:03:44,579 --> 00:03:45,940
I couldn't come back because of the epidemic.

64
00:03:46,220 --> 00:03:47,899
[Now we're going to bring you]

65
00:03:47,899 --> 00:03:49,139
[a major financial news.]

66
00:03:49,139 --> 00:03:51,299
Chairman of Su's Art Gallery, Su Junmin,

67
00:03:51,299 --> 00:03:52,980
died of a heart attack.

68
00:03:52,980 --> 00:03:54,100
Su's Art Gallery was exposed

69
00:03:54,100 --> 00:03:56,299
to have exhibited counterfeit artworks,

70
00:03:56,459 --> 00:03:57,859
causing public outrage.

71
00:03:58,139 --> 00:03:59,859
The stock price of Su's Art Gallery plummeted,

72
00:04:00,019 --> 00:04:02,179
and many partners terminated their cooperation.

73
00:04:02,179 --> 00:04:03,260
Su Junmin has always made

74
00:04:03,260 --> 00:04:05,179
outstanding contributions and reputation in the field of art.

75
00:04:05,179 --> 00:04:05,820
His death

76
00:04:05,820 --> 00:04:07,899
left the entire art world in deep mourning.

77
00:04:07,899 --> 00:04:08,980
[We witnessed a major event]

78
00:04:08,980 --> 00:04:10,299
[in the business world,]

79
00:04:10,299 --> 00:04:12,060
[which also raised questions about]

80
00:04:12,060 --> 00:04:13,220
[the current art market's regulations.]

81
00:04:13,220 --> 00:04:15,180
[Gu Group successfully acquired Su's Art Gallery.]

82
00:04:15,180 --> 00:04:16,659
[This undoubtedly had a profound impact]

83
00:04:16,659 --> 00:04:18,420
[on the entire industry.]

84
00:04:21,899 --> 00:04:22,779
Su Wan.

85
00:04:38,860 --> 00:04:39,659
Wan.

86
00:04:40,779 --> 00:04:41,979
No matter what happens,

87
00:04:43,740 --> 00:04:44,860
I'll always be with you.

88
00:04:47,820 --> 00:04:49,420
We've always been friendly with the Gu family.

89
00:04:50,740 --> 00:04:51,620
Tell me

90
00:04:52,700 --> 00:04:53,500
what you want to do.

91
00:04:55,740 --> 00:04:56,539
I'll help you.

92
00:04:57,620 --> 00:04:58,700
I want revenge.

93
00:05:00,740 --> 00:05:01,820
From that moment on,

94
00:05:01,820 --> 00:05:03,339
I decided to take revenge.

95
00:05:04,860 --> 00:05:06,420
But it was also at this time

96
00:05:06,579 --> 00:05:08,139
that I could study you well

97
00:05:08,300 --> 00:05:10,500
and came up with the plan to enter your family.

98
00:05:11,060 --> 00:05:11,979
Gu Qisen,

99
00:05:12,459 --> 00:05:15,459
Fortunately, you have an illegitimate daughter

100
00:05:15,740 --> 00:05:16,779
named Liu Xiaoxue.

101
00:05:17,339 --> 00:05:19,380
Otherwise, my plan wouldn't be so perfect.

102
00:05:19,779 --> 00:05:20,579
Plastic surgery?

103
00:05:22,899 --> 00:05:23,860
That's absolutely not okay.

104
00:05:23,860 --> 00:05:24,659
It's too dangerous.

105
00:05:26,899 --> 00:05:28,380
This is our last step,

106
00:05:29,300 --> 00:05:30,979
and also the most important step for me.

107
00:05:30,979 --> 00:05:33,180
But you'll ruin yourself.

108
00:05:33,979 --> 00:05:35,219
I've convinced my dad

109
00:05:35,779 --> 00:05:37,500
to agree to my marriage with the Gu family.

110
00:05:38,459 --> 00:05:39,940
I'll help you take back the Su Group,

111
00:05:40,339 --> 00:05:42,219
and everything you want.

112
00:05:42,539 --> 00:05:43,339
Wanqing,

113
00:05:43,979 --> 00:05:45,579
marriage alliances won't solve anything,

114
00:05:45,779 --> 00:05:47,700
and you're too exposed on your own.

115
00:05:48,700 --> 00:05:51,420
I'll enter the Gu family as Ji Xiaoxue,

116
00:05:51,420 --> 00:05:54,139
make the brothers turn against each other,

117
00:05:54,579 --> 00:05:56,659
and bring down the Gu family completely.

118
00:05:58,620 --> 00:06:00,139
That's why I had plastic surgery

119
00:06:00,139 --> 00:06:01,459
to look like your daughter,

120
00:06:02,339 --> 00:06:03,700
and got a snowflake birthmark.

121
00:06:05,539 --> 00:06:06,339
No way.

122
00:06:06,979 --> 00:06:08,180
You are my daughter.

123
00:06:08,380 --> 00:06:09,139
I knew

124
00:06:09,139 --> 00:06:10,979
you wouldn't believe me so easily.

125
00:06:11,659 --> 00:06:13,180
So I had already made arrangements.

126
00:06:14,139 --> 00:06:15,700
We found Liu Xiaoxue

127
00:06:16,060 --> 00:06:17,979
and told her everything that happened.

128
00:06:18,539 --> 00:06:19,820
We asked her to help us.

129
00:06:32,779 --> 00:06:33,620
I see.

130
00:06:35,300 --> 00:06:36,339
We found you

131
00:06:36,339 --> 00:06:38,260
just to tell you this.

132
00:06:38,779 --> 00:06:40,539
I wonder if you can help us.

133
00:06:41,459 --> 00:06:43,500
He doesn't deserve to be a father.

134
00:06:44,579 --> 00:06:45,940
You can find me.

135
00:06:45,940 --> 00:06:47,779
Why can't he find me?

136
00:06:48,579 --> 00:06:50,860
He never thought about looking for me.

137
00:06:52,940 --> 00:06:54,219
In my world,

138
00:06:54,380 --> 00:06:55,860
there is no such affection,

139
00:06:55,940 --> 00:06:57,339
and no father.

140
00:06:59,539 --> 00:07:00,659
I can help you.

141
00:07:01,300 --> 00:07:02,459
But I have a condition.

142
00:07:04,180 --> 00:07:04,979
Go ahead.

143
00:07:05,779 --> 00:07:07,700
You can't tell him where I am,

144
00:07:09,019 --> 00:07:10,500
but you have to tell him

145
00:07:11,099 --> 00:07:12,539
that he does have a daughter,

146
00:07:14,060 --> 00:07:15,380
but his daughter

147
00:07:16,180 --> 00:07:17,659
will never have a father.

148
00:07:42,899 --> 00:07:45,139
Even if I can't go back to the way I was,

149
00:07:46,339 --> 00:07:48,060
I will enter your Gu family.

150
00:07:49,139 --> 00:07:50,260
I must find

151
00:07:50,260 --> 00:07:52,300
the evidence of your framing of my family

152
00:07:54,019 --> 00:07:55,139
to clear my father's name.

153
00:08:06,700 --> 00:08:08,060
I knew from the beginning

154
00:08:08,860 --> 00:08:10,339
that when you see me,

155
00:08:10,539 --> 00:08:11,740
you will think of that woman

156
00:08:11,740 --> 00:08:13,500
you once hurt.

157
00:08:14,740 --> 00:08:16,380
But you are suspicious by nature.

158
00:08:16,899 --> 00:08:17,940
You don't know why I suddenly appear

159
00:08:17,940 --> 00:08:19,139
and what I want.

160
00:08:19,339 --> 00:08:21,260
So I deliberately avoid you

161
00:08:21,260 --> 00:08:22,659
to make you not suspect me.

162
00:08:23,139 --> 00:08:25,539
Xiaoxue, do you have any plans later?

163
00:08:25,700 --> 00:08:26,779
I need to talk to you.

164
00:08:28,099 --> 00:08:29,859
I'll give Young Master Yan a massage later.

165
00:08:30,540 --> 00:08:32,820
[I also deliberately make Gu Chengyan and Gu Chengjing]

166
00:08:32,820 --> 00:08:34,700
[think you have other intentions towards me.]

167
00:08:35,459 --> 00:08:37,339
[Until Gu Chengyan falls in love with me.]

168
00:08:37,339 --> 00:08:38,180
Smell it again.

169
00:08:42,300 --> 00:08:43,540
[And after believing]

170
00:08:43,700 --> 00:08:45,339
[you have other intentions towards me...]

171
00:08:45,339 --> 00:08:46,219
Where did you go?

172
00:08:47,060 --> 00:08:48,739
I just went to

173
00:08:51,859 --> 00:08:53,180
change the sheets for Mr. Gu.

174
00:08:54,979 --> 00:08:56,660
Isn't she just an ordinary girl?

175
00:08:59,180 --> 00:09:00,579
Don't you think

176
00:09:01,259 --> 00:09:02,540
Xiaoxue is special?

177
00:09:03,219 --> 00:09:04,180
What are you talking about?

178
00:09:05,300 --> 00:09:07,099
I just showed you my birthmark.

179
00:09:10,219 --> 00:09:11,739
What's that on your neck?

180
00:09:13,780 --> 00:09:15,660
I might have just accidentally scratched it.

181
00:09:18,940 --> 00:09:20,940
In this way, the people supporting him

182
00:09:20,940 --> 00:09:22,579
will find him unreliable.

183
00:09:22,979 --> 00:09:23,700
And,

184
00:09:24,379 --> 00:09:25,820
do you think you can make up for someone's life

185
00:09:25,820 --> 00:09:27,579
with some dirty money?

186
00:09:27,579 --> 00:09:28,300
Take this.

187
00:09:28,300 --> 00:09:29,979
You remind me of an old friend of mine.

188
00:09:30,060 --> 00:09:31,140
I just want to make up for him.

189
00:09:31,140 --> 00:09:32,219
He just wants you

190
00:09:32,219 --> 00:09:33,900
to do him a favor.

191
00:09:33,900 --> 00:09:35,499
Can you stand on the high ground

192
00:09:35,499 --> 00:09:36,660
and say you make up for me?

193
00:09:37,219 --> 00:09:38,379
Is it right?

194
00:09:39,940 --> 00:09:41,060
How ridiculous!

195
00:09:41,140 --> 00:09:42,499
I don't take your money

196
00:09:43,060 --> 00:09:44,420
because I don't want it.

197
00:09:44,859 --> 00:09:46,540
What I want is not money,

198
00:09:47,020 --> 00:09:47,859
but status,

199
00:09:48,259 --> 00:09:49,579
and your shares.

200
00:09:49,579 --> 00:09:51,459
I went abroad this time

201
00:09:52,660 --> 00:09:53,979
to check my body again.

202
00:09:54,780 --> 00:09:55,940
The situation is not good.

203
00:09:57,300 --> 00:09:58,900
I don't have much time left.

204
00:10:00,459 --> 00:10:01,180
Xiaoxue,

205
00:10:02,379 --> 00:10:03,820
I sincerely hope

206
00:10:04,700 --> 00:10:05,739
to do something for you.

207
00:10:05,739 --> 00:10:08,180
Of course, it's not because you have a conscience,

208
00:10:08,180 --> 00:10:10,219
but because you want to die

209
00:10:10,219 --> 00:10:11,180
with dignity.

210
00:10:11,180 --> 00:10:13,140
If you want to do something for me, fine.

211
00:10:14,820 --> 00:10:15,499
Then...

212
00:10:15,499 --> 00:10:16,579
I have decided

213
00:10:16,660 --> 00:10:19,420
to give all my shares to Ji Xiaoxue.

214
00:10:20,619 --> 00:10:21,619
From today,

215
00:10:22,459 --> 00:10:23,820
Xiaoxue is a shareholder of the Gu Group.

216
00:10:23,820 --> 00:10:25,979
Although this is not in my plan,

217
00:10:25,979 --> 00:10:27,020
the result is the same.

218
00:10:27,020 --> 00:10:28,060
You believe me?

219
00:10:28,060 --> 00:10:30,259
No, no, no. I don't believe it.

220
00:10:31,259 --> 00:10:31,979
I don't believe it.

221
00:10:32,739 --> 00:10:34,180
You are not Su Wan.
